      <title>土耳其央行行长更换令人意外，令投资者感到乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/turkey-s-surprise-central-banker-switch-has-investors-optimistic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近看好土耳其的投资者并未因土耳其央行行长的意外离职而感到不安，这表明他们相信总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的个人保证，即转向市场友好型政策将继续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/turkey-s-surprise-central-banker-switch-has-investors-optimistic</guid>
